    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just about motivation though. it's like... the person who wanted that research doesn't even exist anymore. if the career is gone, who am i actually? i'm just a shell of someone who used to be productive. even trying to \"find motivation\" feels like another chore on a list i can't finish. i just want the noise to stop. i just want to not have to carry this weight anymore.",
